    <h1>The St. Regis Sin&#xAD;ga&#xAD;pore&#x2019;s Chen&#xAD;dol Mousse Cake</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200814/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-08-14"><time>2020-08-14</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE HAPPENINGS</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>The limited-edi­tion Chen­dol Mousse Cake ($68 for 1.2kg) has gula melaka-in­fused sponge­cake lay­ers, paired with co­conut bavarois cream brim­ming with chen­dol, red beans and at­tap seeds. It is fin­ished off with a thin layer of co­conut but­ter­cream and sweet­ened co­conut flakes. Avail­able for pickup at Brasserie Les Saveurs (lobby level) and de­liv­ery ($15).</p>
    <p>WHERE: The St. Regis Sin­ga­pore, Lobby Level, 29 Tan­glin Road</p>
    <p>MRT: Or­chard WHEN: Till Aug 31, 9am - 9pm daily TEL: 6506-6888</p>
    <p>INFO: fes­tive-stregissin­ga­pore.od­dle.me/en_SG</p>


